com.scheid.jsondiff.service.compare.component

Class SizeCompare

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.scheid.jsondiff.service.compare.DefaultCompare
      • com.scheid.jsondiff.service.compare.component.SizeCompare
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JsonDiffCompare
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ContentCompare

    @Component
 @Profile(value="size")
public class SizeCompare
extends DefaultCompare
    Size difference implementation for sets of Base64 encoded jsons. Will be the only implementation used if the 'size' profile is active. Compares the binary data size of the provided Element pair's base64 value.
